caption.p: Effects of LH treatment on the mRNA expression levels of inflammatory mediators in SARS-CoV-2-infected Huh-7 cells. A: TNF-α, B: IL-6, C: CCL-2/MCP-1, D: CXCL-10/IP-10. Data are presented as the mean ± SD obtained from three separate experiments. * p < 0.05; ** p < 0.01; *** p < 0.001, compared with mock-treated cells.
